@@ -0,0 +1,219 @@
+---
+name: ad-layer-visualizer
+description: >
+  Visualize a specific transformer decoder layer from an AutoDeploy FX graph text dump
+  as a hierarchical DOT/PNG diagram. Optionally annotate nodes with actual GPU kernel
